    {
      "id": "aRsvdInDmn_ALbGwAh2vF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -628.1511008853004,
      "y": -7020.912854875838,
      "width": 798.49951171875,
      "height": 69,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9sk",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 13796684,
      "version": 265,
      "versionNonce": 852807622,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483715,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Sync是ReentrantLock的抽象静态内部类，继承自AQS(AbstractQueuedSynchronizer) - 抽象\n队列同步器，AQS中定义了锁的基本行为，AQS中用volatile修饰的state表示当前锁重入的\n次数。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Sync是ReentrantLock的抽象静态内部类，继承自AQS(AbstractQueuedSynchronizer) - 抽象队列同步器，AQS中定义了锁的基本行为，AQS中用volatile修饰的state表示当前锁重入的次数。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "yRS10RLVBHR-VwloVn5um",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -628.1511008853004,
      "y": -6923.412854875838,
      "width": 775.779541015625,
      "height": 46,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c9sl",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 259802484,
      "version": 265,
      "versionNonce": 762673050,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483715,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "NonfairSync、FairSync是ReentrantLock的静态内部类，继承ReentrantLock$Sync，\nNonfairSync实现非公平锁，FairSync实现公平锁。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "NonfairSync、FairSync是ReentrantLock的静态内部类，继承ReentrantLock$Sync，NonfairSync实现非公平锁，FairSync实现公平锁。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
