    {
      "id": "mB1yduOghdJ4aLDwhLwva",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3612.141618847384,
      "y": -1161.71723848033,
      "width": 396.4599304199219,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAFw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1809299652,
      "version": 179,
      "versionNonce": 658306182,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483718,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "prev指向：\n1.加入队列时后于next指向\n2.队尾节点取消后于next取消\n3.唤醒获取锁后先于next取消\n4.队中节点取消时取消节点不取消prev\n5.队中被唤醒且前继结点取消，先于next指向",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "prev指向：\n1.加入队列时后于next指向\n2.队尾节点取消后于next取消\n3.唤醒获取锁后先于next取消\n4.队中节点取消时取消节点不取消prev\n5.队中被唤醒且前继结点取消，先于next指向",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "vdMNgTIS-53gWmiIctim9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3611.055773824893,
      "y": -999.8990603612486,
      "width": 396.4599304199219,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#a5d8ff",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAFx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1561144004,
      "version": 66,
      "versionNonce": 782171866,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483718,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "next指向：\n1.加入队列时先于prev指向\n2.队尾节点取消先于prev取消\n3.竞争到锁后后于prev取消\n4.队中节点取消next取消\n5.队中节点取消，前继有效节点后于prev指向",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "next指向：\n1.加入队列时先于prev指向\n2.队尾节点取消先于prev取消\n3.竞争到锁后后于prev取消\n4.队中节点取消next取消\n5.队中节点取消，前继有效节点后于prev指向",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
