    {
      "id": "8CMst2aNql31gwU_LSU42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 595.2468813130608,
      "y": 3263.2142301921613,
      "width": 872.8997192382812,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "x1LKqLzvjKfv6wWW7Y6mi",
        "b7FZxHfYKZpPmR7ermCYF"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAPW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 116429380,
      "version": 723,
      "versionNonce": 797472198,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483719,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "T1时刻：t3释放许可（head.ws=0->负责唤醒t1），t1获得许可，remaining=0，t1此时不唤醒t2，\nT2时刻：t4释放许可\n    C1：得到头节点head，发现ws=0，不负责唤醒t1，但是要告诉t1需要传播唤醒，\n        设置head.ws=-3。t1判断传播时，满足oldHead.ws<0,唤醒t2；\n    C2：得到头节点t1，t1.ws=-1,于是t4负责唤醒t2；\n    C3：得到头节点head，此时t1早早执行完唤醒，跑路了，t4设置head.ws=-3未被t1采纳，\n        t4设置完判断当前头结点为t1，不等于head，重复C2过程；\nT3时刻：t1、t2已经退出队列，t2坑位晋升为新的头节点，t6入队\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "T1时刻：t3释放许可（head.ws=0->负责唤醒t1），t1获得许可，remaining=0，t1此时不唤醒t2，\nT2时刻：t4释放许可\n    C1：得到头节点head，发现ws=0，不负责唤醒t1，但是要告诉t1需要传播唤醒，\n        设置head.ws=-3。t1判断传播时，满足oldHead.ws<0,唤醒t2；\n    C2：得到头节点t1，t1.ws=-1,于是t4负责唤醒t2；\n    C3：得到头节点head，此时t1早早执行完唤醒，跑路了，t4设置head.ws=-3未被t1采纳，\n        t4设置完判断当前头结点为t1，不等于head，重复C2过程；\nT3时刻：t1、t2已经退出队列，t2坑位晋升为新的头节点，t6入队\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yzG5CaN1QnfhStIjlF9AR",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 592.2086246516762,
      "y": 3185.0464040808247,
      "width": 235.6598358154297,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "x1LKqLzvjKfv6wWW7Y6mi",
        "b7FZxHfYKZpPmR7ermCYF"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAPX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2028981372,
      "version": 77,
      "versionNonce": 1136079258,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483719,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "情况：均只需一个许可\n等待队列：head t1 t2(tail)\n持有许可线程t3、t4",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "情况：均只需一个许可\n等待队列：head t1 t2(tail)\n持有许可线程t3、t4",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "YHQZZ1k2GKfAjbK5q90ZO",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 857.2443295931628,
      "y": 3112.4484749281246,
      "width": 590.973152779352,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "b7FZxHfYKZpPmR7ermCYF"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cAPY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1654248700,
      "version": 184,
      "versionNonce": 1539427590,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767595483719,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "总结：\n1.头节点ws<0或者有许可剩余就委托函数doReleaseShared唤醒后\n续节点（发起唤醒请求）\n2.doReleaseShared会去判断队列中是否有节点需要唤醒（实际唤\n醒）",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "总结：\n1.头节点ws<0或者有许可剩余就委托函数doReleaseShared唤醒后续节点（发起唤醒请求）\n2.doReleaseShared会去判断队列中是否有节点需要唤醒（实际唤醒）",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "bVsceEdcygQbAYgUlm9tA",
